properties.headline: High Wind Warning issued January 7 at 10:51AM MST until January 7 at 2:00PM MST by NWS Riverton WY
properties.description:
...High winds expected through 2 PM this afternoon from South Pass
to Jeffrey City to Casper...

* WHAT...Southwest winds 30 to 40 mph with gusts up to 60 to 65
mph.

* WHERE...Natrona County Lower Elevations.

* WHEN...Until 2 PM MST this afternoon.

* IMPACTS...Damaging winds may blow down trees and power lines. Travel
will be difficult, especially for high profile vehicles.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Outer Drive just south of Casper will be
the most likely areas in the Casper area to experience the 60 to
65 mph wind gusts.
properties.instruction:
People should avoid being outside around trees and branches. Use
caution if you must drive.

NWSheadline: HIGH WIND WARNING IN EFFECT UNTIL 2 PM MST THIS AFTERNOON
